>>> Features <<<
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Use images for show choices command. Modify this by editing Pictures\UI\Archeia Engine LEDA\Choice_[ImageName]
- A JSON file where you can modify the font properties of Show Choices Command.

Changelog:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
** Updated VNM to Version 1.0.1077
